name: space walrus 3000MMM
description:
space walrus 3000 thanks for trying this game! made in a week for Godot Wild Jam #48 READ THIS IF HAVING TROUBLE WITH SHELLS
  • there are 12 shells spread across the map, 4 in each main area (blue, green, pink)
  • each area is accessible from the next, so you can go back and collect any you may have missed
  • shells are optional but allow access to a secret area and ending if you collect them all
